sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as 客户端进程
    participant AMS as system_server<br/>(AMS/ActiveServices)
    participant Service as Service 进程

    Client->>AMS: bindService(intent, conn, flags)<br/>将 ServiceConnection 包装为<br/>IServiceConnection Binder

    AMS->>AMS: retrieveServiceLocked()<br/>通过 PMS 解析 intent<br/>找到 ServiceRecord

    alt Service 进程未启动
        AMS->>Service: Zygote fork 进程<br/>attachApplication()
    end

    alt Service 未创建
        AMS->>Service: scheduleCreateService()<br/>反射创建 Service 实例
        Service->>Service: Service.onCreate()
    end

    AMS->>Service: scheduleBindService(intent)

    Service->>Service: Service.onBind(intent)<br/>返回 IBinder 对象

    Service->>AMS: publishService(token, intent, binder)<br/>将 IBinder 回传给 AMS

    AMS->>AMS: publishServiceLocked()<br/>查找所有绑定该 Service<br/>的 ConnectionRecord

    AMS->>Client: IServiceConnection.connected()<br/>通过 Binder 回调客户端

    Client->>Client: Handler.post → 切到主线程<br/>ServiceConnection<br/>.onServiceConnected(name, binder)

    Note over Client,Service: 此后客户端通过 IBinder 直接与 Service 通信（同进程直接调用，跨进程走 Binder）
